/**
 * This is a port to GLSL of the GEGL Spherize image processing operation.
 *
 * Author: pschroen
 *
 * GEGL Spherize:
 *   http://gegl.org/operations/gegl-spherize.html
 *   https://docs.gimp.org/2.10/en/gimp-filter-spherize.html
